      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "FRANKLIN, INDIANA",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "20 January 1953",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Director Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "I would first like to apologize for writing to you direct, however, I have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "cleared this morning with our State Director and he suggests this procedure.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "We have been having some success with our Ground Observation Corps as we have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "four (4) posts here in the county.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Last Fall I was contacted by one of our local business men wanting to know if",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "I would be interested in joining the International Flying Saucer Bureau. I told him",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "that I would and did join with the idea fully in mind of having the local people who",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "are interested in Flying Saucers also work in our Civil Defense Program. We are",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "only too willing to co-operate in any way we can with Civil Defense. The city of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Franklin is approximately twenty (20) miles southwest of Indianapolis, on the dual",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "lane highway U S #31.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "I am enclosing a letter which was received last October, as well as the current",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "issue of [unclear] REVIEW. Would like to know if this organization has been cleared or",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "is subversive in any way.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "I would appreciate your expediting this information back to us so that we will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "know what steps to take in further enlisting interested persons in our program.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "If you do not require the enclosures please return them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
